channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-21156] SharedWorkOptimizer may preserve filter in TS incorrectly
item.description: For some scan reutilizations, we may end up with a Filter expression associated with the scan that should be removed by the optimizer. This can lead to incorrect results. Repro case is part of the patch.
item.summary: SharedWorkOptimizer may preserve filter in TS incorrectly

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
